  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Bridal & Events Hairstylist",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a talented and creative <em><strong>Bridal &amp; Event Hairstylist </strong></em>with an eye for detail and a passion for bridal beauty and enhancing our clients’ confidence.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Position:</strong> Bridal Hairstylist<br>\n<strong>Location:</strong> [Touch Of Trend Bridal]<br>\n<strong>Employment Type:</strong> [Part-time / Freelance ]</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide professional bridal hairstyling for brides, bridal parties, and special events.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with makeup artists and stylists to deliver cohesive looks.</li>\n  <li>Stay updated with current bridal hairstyle trends and techniques.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of tools and workstations.</li>\n  <li>Offer trials and consultations to brides ahead of their wedding day.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven experience as a hairstylist, preferably in bridal styling.</li>\n  <li>Strong portfolio showcasing bridal or event hairstyling.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of various hairstyling techniques (updos, curls, braids, modern and traditional styles).</li>\n  <li>Good communication and customer service skills.</li>\n  <li>Punctual, professional, and able to work under pressure.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work on weekends and during wedding peak seasons.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>A supportive and creative working environment.</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to grow within the bridal beauty industry.</li>\n  <li>Competitive remuneration (details to be discussed during interview).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’re passionate about helping brides look and feel their best on their big day, we’d love to hear from you!</p>",
