    "description": "<p>Touch Of Trend is created by well-known Myanmar celebrity fashion &amp; make-up artist Khin San Win &amp; two Myanmar aspiring business ladies from Singapore.<br>\nWe don’t think bridal should be stressful or uncomfortable. We don’t think you should be pressured into not feeling like yourself. We aim to provide custom, unique &amp; memorable wedding experience.<br>\n<br>\nOur dresses are unique, figure flattering and above all comfortable. They are made to stand out in bridal world to salute you for being you.</p>",
